on break of tall grass or short grass:    
    set {_l} to event-block's location
    set {_r} to a random integer between 1 and 2
    drop 1 apple at {_l} if {_r} is 1
    drop 2 apple at {_l} if {_r} is 2

on break of any leaves:
    set {_l} to event-block's location
    set {_r} to a random integer between 0 and 20
    drop 1 apple at {_l} if {_r} is 0
    drop 2 apple at {_l} if {_r} is 20